Description: Discover 30,000+ verified radio stations from around the world
 Most radio apps make you search for stations by name or paste in a stream
 URL. Receiver ships with over 30,000 stations ready to explore — each one
 individually scanned and verified, with duplicates removed and logos fetched
 in proper resolution. Just open the app and start discovering.
 .
 No sign-up. No ads. No popularity rankings deciding what you hear. Just radio.
 .
  * 30,000+ curated stations — deduplicated, scanned, and verified
  * High-quality logos for a clean browsing experience
  * Browse and search by tags, country, or language
  * Save your favourite stations for quick access
  * MP3, AAC, Ogg, and HLS stream support
  * MPRIS integration — control playback from your desktop
  * Session persistence — resume where you left off
  * Translated into 120 languages
